articles.title: Bayern Munich suspend and fine Sadio Mané after he punches Leroy Sané - The Guardian
articles.description: Bayern Munich have suspended Sadio Mané after he punched Leroy Sané in a dressing-room argument after the team’s 3-0 defeat at Manchester City
articles.content:
Bayern Munich have suspended Sadio Mané after he punched Leroy Sané in the face in a dressing-room argument after the teams 3-0 defeat at Manchester City on Tuesday.
